33. Role Description

This is a full-time on-site role located in South East Delhi for a 3D Modeler for product design at Unsung India Foundation. As a 3D Modeler, you will be responsible for creating high-quality 3D Modeler for various products. You will collaborate with a team of artists and designers to bring objects, and environments to life. Your work will contribute to the overall visual storytelling and enhance the overall visual experience.

Qualifications
• Proficiency in 3D Modeling software
• Strong understanding of animation principles and techniques
• Knowledge of lighting, shading, and rendering
• Excellent attention to detail
• Portfolio demonstrating 3D Modeling skills
• Degree in 3D Modeling


34. Key Skills:

3DS Max, Visualization, Adobe Photoshop, Architecture, Design, Interior Design, 3DAnimation, Architecture and Interior Design, 3D Max, 3D Rendering, 3D Modelling, Lumion

Responsibilities and Duties

Responsibilities of a 3D Designer are as follows but not limited to:
• Candidate should have knowledge of 3ds max & Adobe Photoshop for creating compelling presentation visuals for our real estate projects.
• Graphics and Art background is an added advantage
• Specialized experience in Walk through and animation may be an added responsibility.
• Candidate will work on creating sitemaps, beautiful project layouts of the architecture projects of the company.


35. Primary Responsibilities:
• Contribute 3D modeling to a project in a team or individual environment.
• Perform research on the intranet and internet for information required to accurately create a technical 3d model. Research is a main component of the position.
• Liaise with subject matter experts (SME) to obtain information as to how a part functions.
• Maintain departmental modeling standards.
• Perform archiving of models for the department. This includes working with files from others.
• Provide weekly progress report updates for assigned workload.

Qualifications:
• Computer Graphic artist, 3D generalist
• Experience in Unity or other gaming engine including Character Animation, Rigging, Modeling and CAD
• Experience working in Architecture, Interior Design and Graphics Production
• Ability to understand American design and aesthetic


